'''Sitonehɛnzɩ''' (''Stonehenge'') kɛna Kumoɖe sɔsɔyɛ naɖɩyɛ. Kumoɖe sɔsɔyɛ nɖɩ ɖɩkɛ cee wayɩ tɔm wonuu kʋtɔzʋ wonuu ŋgʋ kɩkɛ pɩyɛ taŋgbaʋ yɔ yaa pɩyɛ sɔsɔyɛ yɔ. Kumoɖe ɖɩnɛ, ɖigbelu ɖɩ-taa kɛ matʋʋ ndɩ ndɩ kuluŋgulu kɛ hɛkʋ kaɣʋ.

Pama kumoɖe nɖɩ pɩgbaʋ hɛkʋ -2800 nɛ -1100 mbɩ yɔ kɛ pɛɛ saɣʋʋ wɛɛ yaa alɩwaatʋ taa. Pɩɩkɛ prɔnzɩ(bronze) hɛkʋ nɛ hɛkʋ wɛɛ yaa alɩwaatʋ taa. Ɖɩwɛna yaa ɖi-lone hɔɔlʋʋ taa wɛna kilomɛtɛ waa ɛzɩ hiu nɛ naadozo(13) mbɩ yɔ nɛ Salisbury ɛjaɖɛ nɛ ɖi-hayuu kiŋ hɔɔlʋʋ taa kiŋ.

Nɛ wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʋyɛ hɔɔlʋʋ taa kiŋ lɛ, kumoɖe sɔsɔyɛ Stonehɛnzɩ(Stonehenge) ɖɩnɛ, ɖɩwɛna Amesbury egeetiye kiŋ. Amesbury egeetiye ɖɩnɛ, ɖɩna kumoɖe sɔsɔyɛ Stonehɛnzɩ(Stonehenge) pɛhɛkʋ taa mɛtɛ waa yaa walanzɩ nɛ ɖama talɩɣ ɛzɩ mɛtɛ waa nanaaza(4) mbɩ yɔ.

Amesbury kɛna ajɛɛ anɛyɔ: Wiltshire, nɛ pɩtasɩna Angletɛrɩ(Angleterre) pɛŋgbɛyɛ. Kumoɖe sɔsɔyɛ Stonehɛnzɩ(Stonehenge) tɛtʋ tɩŋgɛ nɛ cromlech Avebury tɛtʋ ɖɔɖɔ wɛna ɛzɩ kilomɛtɛ waa ɛzɩ hiŋ naanaza mbɩ yɔ nɛ hayuu kiŋ hɔɔlʋʋ. Pama pahɩla ɖɔɖɔ kɛ kedeŋa Unesco tɔsʋʋ kozaɣ takayaɣ taa.

Pɛgbɛnda payɩ lɛ, payaɣ takayaɣ n̄ʋʋ tobi size«Stonehɛnzɩ(Stonehenge), Avebury nɛ ŋgbɛyɛ tɛtʋ ɖɩgbɛndɩyɛ(et sites associés)». Sɔnɔ lɛ, tɛtʋ tʋnɛ, tʋhɔŋ saɣɖɛ tɩnaa yaa ɛsɩyɛ egbena n̄ɩma sakɩyɛ. Paa pɩnaɣ ŋga, samaɣ ŋga kowoki yɔ kɔn̄ɔtʋna talɩɣ ɛzɩ miiliyɔɔ kʋɖʋmʋ mbɩ yɔ. Kumoɖe sɔsɔyɛ Stonehɛnzɩ(Stonehenge) ɖɩnɛ paasɩma-ɖɩ hooo hooo kɛ hɛkʋ nɛ hɛkʋ wɛɛ yaa alɩwaatʋ taa.

 
